Screen Resolution, DPI (dots per inch), Full Screen, Tor Browser window size (maximization?)
}}

= Recommended Screen Resolution =
* <u>Recommended:</u> Use screen resolution <code>1920x1080</code>.
* <u>Rationale:</u> See forum discussion: [https://forums.whonix.org/t/make-screen-resolution-1920x1080-by-default-for-all-vms/9143 Make screen resolution 1920x1080 by default for all VMs]

= Default Screen Resolution =
* <u>Note:</u> Default screen resolution is platform specific.
* <u>{{non_q_project_name_short}}:</u> VirtualBox and KVM use <code>1920x1080</code> by default.
* <u>{{q_project_name_short}}:</u> Depends on dom0.

= Full Screen Recommendation =
* <u>Note:</u> Full screen recommendation is platform specific.
* <u>{{non_q_project_name_short}}:</u> Virtualizers VirtualBox and KVM do not use full screen by default. It is recommended to use [[Desktop#Use_Full-screen_Mode|Use Full-screen Mode]].
* <u>{{q_project_name_short}}:</u> Uses full screen by default. [[Desktop#Avoid_VM_Full_Screen_Mode|Avoid VM Full Screen Mode is discouraged]].

= Tor Browser Window Size =
* <u>Avoid:</u> Maximize or resize the Tor Browser window.
* <u>Rationale:</u> See [[Tor_Browser#browser_window_size|browser window size]].
* <u>Keep:</u> Default window size.

= DPI =
* <u>Avoid:</u> Change DPI settings.
* <u>Keep:</u> Default DPI settings.

= Custom Settings =
* <u>Question:</u> Do custom settings negatively affect anonymity?
* <u>Note:</u> This is [[Unspecific|unspecific to {{project_name_short}}]].
* <u>Note:</u> This depends on [[Tor Browser]]. Therefore this question is best redirected to Tor Browser as per [[Self Support First Policy]].
* <u>Recommendation:</u> For abundance of caution, reasonable default settings are recommended on this page.
* <u>Forum discussion:</u> [https://forums.whonix.org/t/will-custom-dpi-dots-per-inch-values-negatively-affect-my-anonymity/20204 Will custom dpi (dots per inch) values negatively affect my anonymity?]

